ation+Quarterly&amp;rft.atitle=Review+Essay%3A+From+Oppression+to+Hope%3A+Freire%27s+Journey+Toward+Utopia&amp;rft.volume=29&amp;rft.pages=115-124&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.aulast=Collins&amp;rft.aufirst=Denis+E.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APedagogy+of+Hope%3A+Reliving+Pedagogy+of+the+Oppressed\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-:0-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_6-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_6-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Hendriks, Sarah. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://fcis.oise.utoronto.ca/~daniel_sc/freire/sh.html\">\"Pedagogy of Hope: Reliving Pedagogy of the Oppressed. (Review)\"</a>. <i>Reviews of Paolo Freire's Books</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-05-18</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Reviews+of+Paolo+Freire%27s+Books&amp;rft.atitle=Pedagogy+of+Hope%3A+Reliving+Pedagogy+of+the+Oppressed.+%28Review%29&amp;rft.aulast=Hendriks&amp;rft.aufirst=Sarah&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Ffcis.oise.utoronto.ca%2F~daniel_sc%2Ffreire%2Fsh.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APedagogy+of+Hope%3A+Reliving+Pedagogy+of+the+Oppressed\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Fowler, Shelli B. (1998). \"<span style=\"padding-left:0.2em;\">\"</span>Under the Shade of this Mango Tree\": Reflections on a Pedagogical Practice that Crosses Disciplinary Boundaries\". <i>Quest</i>. <b>50</b> (3): 319\u2013323.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt